{
  "stem": "20084.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they were searching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were searching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The kapos were searching what we have on our possession.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were looking everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Under you arms, in your body, they were checking or you don't have anything, some jewelry or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they're looking around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I saw father and Bernard also standing in one of the lines to get into to the, to the, to the showers, delouse and whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I think this was the last time that I saw my father in Mauthausen, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] and, and Bernard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Well, then after the shower, we were assigned-- I don't know what happened to Father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were assigned to Gusen I.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Gusen I was just like a suburb, like maybe a couple miles, two, three miles, outside of Mauthausen, the main camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we were assigned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we worked in the granite, granite quarry every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We had to march to the granite quarry and break up rocks and load it into the, into the lorries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And, and coming back, we had to march, and carrying the dead ones or the wounded ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because they check how many left the place and how many went through the gate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And this was-- the rock quarry was down below.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And above, there were towers with German guards with the machine guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And when they were feeling like a little excitement for them, they were shooting down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So you never looked up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And you never knew where you were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because you never-- you always were afraid to look up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Because they were always shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Well, work was very, very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And it was in winter without gloves [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Not in winter-- I mean, it was already [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] September, October.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
